org.apache.hadoop.hive.shims

Interface HadoopShims.HdfsEncryptionShim

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Hadoop23Shims.HdfsEncryptionShim, HadoopShims.NoopHdfsEncryptionShim
    Enclosing interface:
    HadoopShims

    public static interface HadoopShims.HdfsEncryptionShim
    This interface encapsulates methods used to get encryption information from HDFS paths.

      • comparePathKeyStrength

        int comparePathKeyStrength(org.apache.hadoop.fs.Path path1,
                           org.apache.hadoop.fs.Path path2)
                    throws IOException
        Compares two encrypted path strengths.
        Parameters:
        path1 - HDFS path to compare.
        path2 - HDFS path to compare.
        Returns:
        1 if path1 is stronger; 0 if paths are equals; -1 if path1 is weaker.
        Throws:
        IOException - If an error occurred attempting to get encryption/key metadata
